{"id":"errors/NG1001","title":"NG1001: 裝飾器引數不是物件字面量。","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2mlypxsgmbem9m1fyt6l5dtrn\">NG1001: 裝飾器引數不是物件字面量。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dnprtcvl45sdpq963yd0dhl7f\">這是 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\">Ivy 中的有意更改</a>，與 View Engine 相比，它對裝飾器強制執行更嚴格的引數要求。 Ivy 需要這種方法，因為它透過將表示式移到類別輸出中的其他位置來編譯這些裝飾器。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7uv8ma5nzs00q7gq4lcn5qmqm\">這是 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\">Ivy 中的有意更改</a>，與 View Engine 相比，它對裝飾器強制執行更嚴格的引數要求。Ivy 需要這種方法，因為它透過將表示式移到類別輸出中的其他位置來編譯這些裝飾器。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1fxd4knjc0bc83t0i2mr9nevb\">把所有宣告：</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nconst moduleDefinition = {…}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>(moduleDefinition)\nexport class AppModule {\n    constructor() {}\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6w60t5chl4u5c0hug0y16j0g8\">移入裝飾器：</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({…})\nexport class AppModule {\n    constructor() {}\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Injectable\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/Pipe\n - errors/NG1001#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG1001#description\n - errors/NG1001#ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\n-->"}